               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Fǝtḥa nagaśt “Justice of the Kings” (fols. 5ra-146rc)&#xD; -
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-8rc)&#xD; - Table of contents (fols. 8rc-8vb)&#xD; -
                     Ecclesiastical laws (fols. 8vb-58vc)&#xD; - Civil laws (fols. 59ra-142vb)&#xD;
                     - Law of Patriarch Cyril concerning land transaction (fols. 142vc-146rc)&#xD;
                     &#xD; Colophon.</summary>
